<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078266>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., adult, SEM micrographs: A—dorsal view; B—ventral view; C—ventrolateral view; D—dorsoanterior view; E—posterior view; F—notogastral tuberculate microsculpturing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078268>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., dissected adult, microscope images: A—lamellar cusps, dorsal view; B—anterior part of prodorsum, lateral view; C—dorsophragmata; D—notogastral porose area Aa; E—notogastral seta lm; F genital plates and part of epimeral and lateral podosomal region, ventral view; G—part of anoadanal region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078268/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078262>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., adult:A—dorsal view (legs not shown); B—ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown); C—lateral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown); D—posterior view. Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078262/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078264>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., adult: A—subcapitulum, ventral view; B—palp, right, antiaxial view; C—chelicera, left, paraxial view; D—leg I, right, antiaxial view; E —leg II (tarsus not shown), right, antiaxial view; F—leg III (tarsus not shown), left, antiaxial view; D—leg IV, left, antiaxial view. Scale bars 50 μm (A, C–G), 20 μm (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078286>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., SEM micrographs of slightly deformed deutonymph (A–C) and microscope images of dissected juvenile instars (D–H): A, B—dorsal view; C—lateral view; D—larva, dorsal view; E—tritonymph, basal part of prodorsum and anterior part of gastronotum (pigmented, small, round pit (? rudimentary porose area Aa) is indicated by an arrow), dorsal view; F—tritonymph, some setae on gastronotic macrosclerite, dorsal view; G—protonymph, anterior part of body, ventral view; H —protonymph, posterior part of body, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078286/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078270>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., juvenile instars: A—larva, dorsal view; B—protonymph, dorsal view. Scale bar 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078270/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078274>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., juvenile instars: A—larva, lateral view; B—tritonymph, lateral view. Scale bar 50 μm. Scale bars 50 μm (A), 100 μm (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078280>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., tritonymph: A—dorsal view; B—ventral view (legs and anterior part of body not shown). Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078280/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078278>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., ventral side of juvenile instars (legs and anterior part of body not shown): A—larva; B—protonymph; C—deutonymph. Scale bars 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078278/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078284>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov., larva: A—subcapitulum, ventral view; B—palp, right, antiaxial view; C—chelicera, left, paraxial view; D—leg I, left, paraxial view; E—leg II, left, paraxial; F—leg III, left, antiaxial view. Scale bars 10 μm (A–C), 20 μm (D–F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078284/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7078288>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Collecting place of Oromurcia magadanensis sp. nov.: A—landscape of the Ola Plateau, Magadan Region, 60°39’ N, 151°16’ E; B—snowbed in the stream gully (the place of collection, 1023 m a.s.l., is indicated by an yellow arrow); C, D—rocky slope of a snowbed with vegetation patches dominated by Oxyria digyna and Artemisia kruhsiana (C) or Ranunculus pygmaeus and Sanionia uncinata (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7078288/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

